name: Last Epistle
description:
I was her older sister...

she's the perfect one from our family...

time passes so quickly...

my existance is already got forgotten...

she said I was kind towards those people... 

but in the end...

she's the one who against me...

I am the daughter of kitsune clan...

would end this war...

and this is was our consequence for being a twins...

in our family...

- Seeker of The Darkness.
